        "code": "public double positionPixelToGu(int pixels, int index) {\n    double l = lengthToGu(pixels, Units.PX);\n    switch(index) {\n        case 0:\n            l -= graphWidthGU() / 2.0;\n            l = (hi.x + lo.x) / 2.0 + l;\n            break;\n        case 1:\n            l -= graphHeightGU() / 2.0;\n            l = (hi.y + lo.y) / 2.0 + l;\n            break;\n        default:\n            throw new IllegalArgumentException();\n    }\n    logger.fine(String.format(\"%spixel[%d] %d --> %fgu\", this, index, pixels, l));\n    return l;\n}"
